description: The K100 model by Sanjo is one of our iconic designs, boasting over 90 years of history. It has been reinvented to celebrate the original while preserving some of its key features: a canvas upper and a stitched logo on the side. To make this model even more special, we've revolutionized it with modern details and higher-quality materials: a textile tag on the tongue, full inner lining, cushioned insole, coated eyelets, and a TPR outsole offering excellent durability, abrasion resistance, and lightweight properties. Made in Portugal COMPOSITION Upper: 100% Organic Cotton Canvas, resistant to sunlight. Sole: 100% Vegan TPR Insole: Memory foam Lining: Mesh VEGAN INESCOPEnsures the main chemical nature of the material does not include fibers of animal origin (such as hides, leather, silk, wool, or down). CARBON FOOTPRINTAdherence to a carbon footprint reduction plan, with specific actions to lower IEC emissions released into the atmosphere during manufacturing. GLOBAL ORGANIC TEXTILE STANDARDWith the GOTS certification, we ensure compliance with social, environmental, health, and safety standards. We prioritize workplace safety and value certified fabrics across all our markets.

description: The K100 model by Sanjo is one of our iconic designs, boasting over 90 years of history. It has been reinvented to celebrate the original while preserving some of its key features: a canvas upper and a stitched logo on the side. To make this model even more special, we've revolutionized it with modern details and higher-quality materials: a textile tag on the tongue, full inner lining, cushioned insole, coated eyelets, and a TPR outsole offering excellent durability, abrasion resistance, and lightweight properties. Made in Portugal COMPOSITION Upper: 100% Organic Cotton Canvas, resistant to sunlight. Sole: 100% Vegan TPR Insole: Memory foam Lining: Mesh VEGAN INESCOPEnsures the main chemical nature of the material does not include fibers of animal origin (such as hides, leather, silk, wool, or down). CARBON FOOTPRINTAdherence to a carbon footprint reduction plan, with specific actions to lower IEC emissions released into the atmosphere during manufacturing. GLOBAL ORGANIC TEXTILE STANDARDWith the GOTS certification, we ensure compliance with social, environmental, health, and safety standards. We prioritize workplace safety and value certified fabrics across all our markets.

description: Stay warm and dry on cold and rainy days with Sanjo made from Burel, a water-resistant fabric crafted from 100% natural wool. Born in the heart of Serra da Estrela, Burel has been traditionally used by high-mountain shepherds. Durable and versatile, it transitioned from cloaks and coats for rainy, snowy, and cold mountain days to becoming an essential part of Sanjo's construction. Made in Portugal COMPOSITION Upper: Burel – water-resistant, easy to maintain, eco-friendly, 100% Portuguese Lining: Mesh Sole: 100% Vegan TPR

description: The K100 model by Sanjo is one of our iconic designs, boasting over 90 years of history. It has been reinvented to celebrate the original while preserving some of its key features: a canvas upper and a stitched logo on the side. To make this model even more special, we've revolutionized it with modern details and higher-quality materials: a textile tag on the tongue, full inner lining, cushioned insole, coated eyelets, and a TPR outsole offering excellent durability, abrasion resistance, and lightweight properties. Made in Portugal COMPOSITION Upper: 100% Organic Cotton Canvas, resistant to sunlight. Sole: 100% Vegan TPR Insole: Memory foam Lining: Mesh VEGAN INESCOPEnsures the main chemical nature of the material does not include fibers of animal origin (such as hides, leather, silk, wool, or down). CARBON FOOTPRINTAdherence to a carbon footprint reduction plan, with specific actions to lower IEC emissions released into the atmosphere during manufacturing. GLOBAL ORGANIC TEXTILE STANDARDWith the GOTS certification, we ensure compliance with social, environmental, health, and safety standards. We prioritize workplace safety and value certified fabrics across all our markets.

description: The K200 model by Sanjo is one of our iconic designs, boasting over 90 years of history. It has been reinvented to celebrate the original while preserving some of its key features: a canvas upper and a stitched logo on the side. To make this model even more special, we've revolutionized it with modern details and higher-quality materials: a textile tag on the tongue, full inner lining, cushioned insole, coated eyelets, and a TPR outsole offering excellent durability, abrasion resistance, and lightweight properties. Made in Portugal COMPOSITION Upper: 100% Organic Cotton Canvas, resistant to sunlight. Sole: 100% Vegan TPR Insole: Memory foam Lining: Mesh VEGAN INESCOPEnsures the main chemical nature of the material does not include fibers of animal origin (such as hides, leather, silk, wool, or down). CARBON FOOTPRINTAdherence to a carbon footprint reduction plan, with specific actions to lower IEC emissions released into the atmosphere during manufacturing. GLOBAL ORGANIC TEXTILE STANDARDWith the GOTS certification, we ensure compliance with social, environmental, health, and safety standards. We prioritize workplace safety and value certified fabrics across all our markets.

product_title: Sanjo Kids V100 Burel OG // Navy
description: Stay warm and dry on the coldest and rainiest days with the Sanjo Burel, a water-resistant fabric made from 100% natural wool. Born in the heart of Serra da Estrela, Burel has traditionally been used by mountain shepherds. Durable and versatile, it has transitioned from being used for raincoats and jackets on snowy, cold mountain days to becoming part of Sanjo footwear construction. Made in Portugal COMPOSITION Upper: Burel – water-resistant, easy to maintain, eco-friendly, 100% Portuguese Lining: Mesh Sole: 100% Vegan TPR

description: The Desert Boot Sanjo is a boot with a versatile silhouette, rescued from the 50s. It provides functionality and style and stands out for its mesh lining and TR sports sole that provides the comfort of the sneaker. The upper is made of premium suede and traditional leather laces. description: Stay warm and dry on the coldest and rainiest days with Sanjo in Burel, a water-resistant fabric made from 100% natural wool. Born in the heart of Serra da Estrela, Burel is traditionally used by shepherds high up in the mountains. Resistant and versatile, it has become part of the construction of Sanjo from capes and coats for rainy, snowy and cold days in the mountains. Made in Portugal COMPOSITION Upper: Burel – water resistant, easy maintenance, environmentally friendly, 100% Portuguese Lining: Mesh Sole: 100% Vegan TPR

product_title: Sanjo KIDS V100 Burel OG // Yellow
description: Mantém-te quente e seco nos dias mais frios e chuvosos com as Sanjo em Burel, tecido resistente à água e feito em 100% lã natural. Nascido no coração da Serra da Estrela, o Burel é tradicionalmente usado pelos pastores do alto da montanha. Resistente e versátil que, das capas e casacos para os dias de chuva, neve e frio na montanha, passaram a fazer parte da construção das Sanjo.

Mantém\xa0o teu calçado Sanjo guardado num local sem humidade, para melhor conservação.Usa\xa0sabão neutro,\xa0sem lixívias ou detergentes. Limpa\xa0somente a parte externa. Depois de limpar, retira\xa0o sabão com um pano húmido.
Nunca uses máquina de lavar nem deixes o teu calçado Sanjo de molho ou enxagues\xa0na torneira. Usa\xa0sempre o mínimo de água possível.
